{"tid":1801183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又唔比保釋, 第幾單?] 17歲男生在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，申請保釋被拒","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T02:30:39.000Z","uid":155883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3c17718d65a5d7b559d34347272074a708204e","tid":1801183,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:21:32.000Z","msg":"知專生涉藏摺刀被拒保釋<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：犯錯無懲罰 高層包庇前線<br />\n<br />\n首被告代表大律師指，被告遭拘捕後已無反抗，仍遭警員揮棍毆打及噴射胡椒噴霧。署理主任裁判官高偉雄應控方要求將案件押後至2月12日，兩被告獲准保釋，但須守宵禁令及禁足新城市廣場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，同晚警方亦於旺角朗豪坊外施放催淚彈驅散人群，其間截查一名17歲唐姓知專設計學院男生，在其背囊中搜出一把摺刀及兩個鐵鎚。男生被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，他申請保釋被拒，須還柙至2月20日再訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191228/DO2IWUBIN5HLVCG7FX76TX5TR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191228%2FDO2IWUBIN5HLVCG7FX76TX5TR4%2F&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=3bee6aa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191228%2FDO2IWUBIN5HLVCG7FX76TX5TR4%2F&h=284e7350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191228/DO2IWUBIN5HLVCG7FX76TX5TR4/</a>"},{"pid":"20b3317ff5a942f753d7511f12a23fa12b8eace2","tid":1801183,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=0ce42391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" 